**Passionate Full Stack Java Developer** with expertise in building scalable, efficient, and maintainable applications. I specialize in Java ecosystem technologies, modern web development, and creating seamless user experiences.

🔹 **Name:** Yatendra Pratap Singh  
🔹 **Title:** Full Stack Java Developer  
🔹 **Location:** India 🇮🇳  
🔹 **Expertise:** Java, Spring Boot, React.js, Database Design  
🔹 **Mission:** Creating robust backend solutions and intuitive user experiences  
🔹 **Philosophy:** Clean code is not just working code - it's art!  
🔹 **Status:** 🟢 Available for exciting opportunities  

### 🚀 Core Specializations
- ☕ **Java & Spring Boot Ecosystem** - Building enterprise-grade applications
- ⚛️ **React.js & Modern Frontend** - Creating responsive user interfaces  
- 🗄️ **Database Design & Optimization** - Efficient data management solutions
- 🔧 **RESTful API Development** - Scalable backend services
- 🏗️ **System Architecture** - Designing maintainable software solutions

